<script>
/* Ensures that the tabs automatically change when hovering over the section */
    var Webflow = Webflow || [];
    Webflow.push(function () {
      // DOMready has fired
      // May now use jQuery and Webflow api

// start everything
      var tabTimeout;
      clearTimeout(tabTimeout);
      tabLoop();

    // Cycle through all tabs. Match class names
    function tabLoop() {
        tabTimeout = setTimeout(function() {
            var $next = $('.header103_tabs-menu').children('.w--current:first').next();

            if($next.length) {
                $next.click();  // user click resets timeout
            } else {
                $('.header103_tab-link:first').click();
            }
        }, 6000);  // 6 second tab loop (change this)
    }

    // Reset loop if a tab is clicked
    $('.header103_tab-link').click(function() {
        clearTimeout(tabTimeout);
        tabLoop();
        });
    });
</script>

<style>                                  
.standard-tab {
  -webkit-touch-callout: none; /* iOS Safari */
    -webkit-user-select: none; /* Safari */
     -khtml-user-select: none; /* Konqueror HTML */
       -moz-user-select: none; /* Firefox */
        -ms-user-select: none; /* Internet Explorer/Edge */
            user-select: none; /* Non-prefixed version, currently
                                  supported by Chrome and Opera */                                  
</style>
